.container-fluid.container-margin.platform-cover-container
  .platform-cover.landing-cover
    .fixed-bg-slide
      .imgbg.stars-cover
  .container.landing-cover-detail
    .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.mt-60
      .center-text
        %h1
          TO SPACE, TOGETHER
        %h3
          We are building a decentralized space program, connecting thousands of engineers, scientists, and future astronauts, to devise and fund next-generation space initiatives. 
  .container.mt-20.mb-30
    %h2.section-title.center-text How it Works
    #how-it-works.container.platform-show-container
      .row
        .col-md-15
          .col-md-12.how-box.space-col
            = inline_svg('how/brainstorm.svg', title: 'co-owner', class: 'how-icon')
            %h3 STEP 1
            %h2 Define Projects
            %ul
              %li Initial collaboration is fostered through the community-driven curation of a portfolio of projects 
              %li Requirements and goals are defined for the projects in order to guide the solution stage
        .col-md-15
          .col-md-12.how-box.space-col
            = inline_svg('how/build.svg', title: 'code', class: 'how-icon')
            %h3 STEP 2
            %h2 Create Solutions
            %ul
              %li Community members are incentivized to submit open-source action plans through a competitive “request for proposals” process
              %li Action plans are vetted using a transparent decision-making process 
        .col-md-15
          .col-md-12.how-box.space-col
            = inline_svg('how/solutions.svg', title: 'donate', class: 'how-icon')
            %h3 STEP 3
            %h2 Catalog Plans
            %ul
              %li The best proposal for each project will be added to a digital commons, with alternates archived
              %li Everyone will have access to these shared commons and will be enabled to take action
            %br
        .col-md-15
          .col-md-12.how-box.space-col
            = inline_svg('how/fund.svg', title: 'donate', class: 'how-icon')
            %h3 STEP 4
            %h2 Raise Funding
            %ul
              %li Funds are collectively raised to support the development, testing, and launch of top action plans
              %li Jobs are created and work contracts are assigned based on solution proposals   
            %br
        .col-md-15
          .col-md-12.how-box.space-col
            = inline_svg('how/launch.svg', title: 'donate', class: 'how-icon')
            %h3 STEP 5
            %h2 Engines On
            %ul
              %li Collaborative research and shared visions become realities
              %li Contributions are rewarded upon commercial adoption of solutions seeded from the digital commons   
            %br
